-------
- Streaming pipeline between source and destination; no temp files created.
WP-CLI
------
search-replace https://local.test -> https://staging.test
Command   : [local] (cd tests/fixtures/staging) "wp" "search-replace" "https://local.test" "https://staging.test" "--skip-columns=guid"
- WP-CLI search-replace executed successfully.

$ movepress push db local production --yes
? failed
Error: Refusing to run push database from 'local' to 'production' with --yes because 'production' looks like production.
Re-run interactively after a --dry-run preview or set MOVEPRESS_ALLOW_PROD=1 to enable non-interactive approvals.

$ movepress push db local production
? failed
Error: Refusing to run push database from 'local' to 'production' without interactive confirmation because 'production' looks like production.
Launch movepress from a terminal after --dry-run, or pass --yes with MOVEPRESS_ALLOW_PROD=1 for CI.

$ movepress push db local staging
? failed
Error: Refusing to run push database from 'local' to 'staging' without confirmation. Re-run interactively or pass --yes for non-production targets.

$ env MOVEPRESS_ALLOW_PROD=1 PATH="$PWD/tests/fixtures/bin:$PATH" movepress push db local production --yes --config tests/cmd/fixtures/local-production.toml
